            "text": "Today, the family-run museum sits on 35 acres of property located about 50 miles north of Chicago, and it draws in more than 250,000 visitors each year with unique and interesting exhibits that include around 400 cars and displays. Bill Grams' passion for cars is obvious in the collection assembled in the museum as well as the classic and collectible cars offered up through Volo Auto Sales. The Volo Auto Museum is planning a memorial exhibit in Bill's honor. ",
